    "However, due to the language barriers and inequality of digital resources across languages, there is an urgent need for knowledge transformation, such as from one human language to another (13, 14).",
    "Thus, to help address digital health inequalities, machine translation (MT) technologies can be of good use in this case.",
    "MT is one of the earliest artificial intelligence (AI) branches dating back to the 1950s, and it has gained a boom with other natural language processing (NLP) tasks in recent years due to the newly designed powerful learning model Transformers (15) (16) (17) (18).",
